      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition driver that appears to have been cared for and is ready to be enjoyed, but it is not a mint/show-quality example. The exterior should present well overall with the kind of light cosmetic wear and minor age-related flaws you\u2019d expect on a used vehicle, and the interior should be in nice, well-kept shape without being perfect. A buyer can expect a solid, presentable car that feels like a properly maintained driver rather than a project or rough car.",
