    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver with honest appeal and plenty of potential for its next owner. This car presents respectably overall and can be enjoyed as-is, but it does show age and will likely need some cosmetic and/or mechanical attention over time. A good opportunity for someone looking for an affordable entry point into ownership without paying top-tier money.",
