    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t trying to be showroom-perfect, but it\u2019s an affordable way to get into something you can tinker with, use as a backup, or turn into a solid little project. It\u2019s got character, a straightforward no-nonsense feel, and at this price it makes a lot of sense for someone who sees the opportunity rather than just the cosmetics. If you want something budget-friendly and easy to be realistic about, come have a look.",
